  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nNoticed my node was offline. Looked at the history and it shows \"SyncedKilled\" : (last line not shown as it just shows lighthouse dir after the beacon node closed)\r\n![Screenshot from 2020-09-28 21-38-09](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/25303159/94440125-d9e01280-01d3-11eb-8d89-5090b11ba922.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n## Version\r\nLighthouse/v0.2.11-a97ec318\r\nI build from source. \r\n\r\n\r\n## Present Behavior\r\n\r\nIt is working. (Previously running for many weeks without issue. First time seeing this.)\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nNot randomly shut down.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nStart the beacon node again.\r\n\r\n## System Specs\r\n\r\nx64, Ubuntu Desktop 20.04, 16 GB Ram, Rx-427bb Ã— 4 CPU\r\n\r\n##  Apps running\r\n\r\nPrysm, LIghthouse, Geth, Firefox, Astrill VPN\r\n",
